data.description: This home is eligible for USDA benefits.  It provides an open concept living, dining, and kitchen living.  The kitchen island provides additional counterspace for meal prep and entertainment.  The home does have a split floorplan with a large primary bath and closet.  The additional rooms are separated by a second full bath.  This home does have an attached one car garage with utility options.  Come take a look for yourself and see if this home is right for you. All offers will be considered.
